      "date": "2013-08-26 06:03:53.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nI think the patch is some hack, any will introduce security hole. There may be UID/GID mapping on MDT side, so even if you specify the special case as root user, it still possible be mapped to another user in the future. It is MDT to decide how to handle such case.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
