        "subject": "LU-3727 nfs: Fix ll_get_parent() LBUG caused by permission",
        "message": "LU-3727 nfs: Fix ll_get_parent() LBUG caused by permission\n\nWhen ll_get_parent() is trying to get the attributes of parent\ndirectory, it will hit LBUG if NFS daemon user does not have the\nexecute permission of the child directory.\n\nThis patch fixes the problem by set the UID/GID to root for\nll_get_parent().\n\nSigned-off-by: Li Xi <lixi@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: If5f4b2d18a6fdb1e51fd61e8819f465ad0db9fe0\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
